             TO TEMP-IDX
 
           CALL cavinpth USING
               PATH-IDX
               CAVE-CONN(CAVE-IDX,CONN-IDX)
               CAVE-IN-PATH-SW
           END-CALL

           EVALUATE TRUE                    ALSO TRUE
             WHEN   CAVE-IS-BIG(TEMP-IDX)   ALSO ANY
             WHEN   CAVE-IS-SMALL(TEMP-IDX) ALSO NOT CAVE-IN-PATH
                    CALL findpath USING
                        FIND-PATH-AREAS
                    END-CALL
           END-EVALUATE
